'.'
'Azure Application Insights \xc2\xa3 : Stores monitoring and diagnostics information. For'
'more information, see Monitor online endpoints.'
'\xc2\xae Note'
'You can delete the Application Insights instance after cluster creation if you'
'want. Deleting it limits the information gathered from the workspace, and'
'may make it more difficult to trouleshoot prolems. If you delete the'
'Application Insights instance created y the workspace, you cannot re-'
'create it without deleting and recreating the workspace.'
'\xc2\x7 Azure Key Vault : Stores secrets that are used y compute targets and other'
"sensitive information that's needed y the workspace."
